data.description: Well cared for Eaglewood home with many updates completed over the years!  No shortage of room to sprawl with 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, & 2 large living areas!  Spacious kitchen w/ upgraded cabinets, granite counters, & SS appliances.  Property is tucked away on cul-de-sac w/ fenced in yard, large deck, & shed.  Easy access to miles of lighted trail system & excellent commutable location!Several big ticket items have been completed over the years and not original to the home to include all windows, kitchen update, garage door, furnace, lighting, flooring, & paint.  Enjoy the comfort of the wood burning stove in the upstairs main living area w/ partial mountain views.  Updated wood stove surround, LVP flooring, lighting, & paint over recent years have been completed in the main living areas.  The dining area is open to the oversized large kitchen with plenty of room to move about and entertain.  Easy access to the large deck that is perfect for entertaining.    The primary suite upstairs includes a private bathroom and walk in closet.  Three bedrooms are located upstairs, and a fourth bedroom is located in the lower level.  The lower living area is the larger of the 2 living areas and has a gas fired fireplace to take the chill out of the air.  The laundry room includes the built in shelving and washer/dryer stay.  The 4th bedroom in the lower level is oversized and has easy access to the lower level main bathroom.  Perfect for guests or generational living!
